TUI Discusses Hapag-Lloyd Sale With Neptune Orient, Welt Says

-- B y   A l e x   W e b b
-- 
2011-12-03T12:04:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-03/tui-discusses-hapag-lloyd-sale-with-neptune-orient-welt-says.html
TUI AG  is in talks with Singaporean
state majority-owned  Neptune Orient Lines Ltd . about the sale of
its stake in container shipping unit Hapag-Lloyd, Die Welt
 reported , without saying where it had got the information.  The two parties will meet for further talks in January as
TUI looks to sell its 38 percent stake in 2012, Welt said.  “It has been widely known since 2008 that we are looking
to sell our shares, and we are evaluating all options,” TUI
spokesman Mario Koepers told Bloomberg by telephone.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 Alex Webb  in Frankfurt 
